p.k: This new episode of One day with presents the private life of one of our new Playboy TV Europe models: Karina Avakyan, from Russia! From her morning routine at a stretching session, in order to improve her body’s flexibility, to a classic photoshoot in the evening. Karina shows a typical day of her life in Moscow and some other new activities such as indoor skydiving. She also shares with you her passion for travelling and talks about the trips she enjoyed the most: London, Paris, Venice, Asia… Don’t miss anything from her everyday life!
